{"tid":2390852,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"劉夢熊：BNO持有人可否獲居英權或申請加入英籍，純屬英國内政，中方無權干涉。","createTime":"2021-02-02T00:16:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-02T12:15:04.000Z","uid":36494,"like":65,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"6c922c1f977d3e99fe6176a028ec5b450e181b01","tid":2390852,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T00:16:19.000Z","msg":"BNO持有人可否獲居英權或申請加入英籍，純屬英國内政，中方無權干涉。至於中國籍香港永久性居民，出入香港、中國内地、澳門，通常只是使用香港身份證、回鄉證，根本不會使用BNO！中国外交部不承認BNO為有效旅游證件，並無實際意義！<br />\n<br />\n問題是，香港持有BNO證件人數高達290萬人。中方和港府取態，明明是國與國爭拗卻回個頭來懲罰這290萬作為工商社會中堅的港人，大失民心，不利於人心回歸！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%BE%97%E6%B0%91%E5%BF%83%E8%80%85%E5%BE%97%E5%A4%A9%E4%B8%8B/?fbclid=IwAR0ZXdawuzg1PYR2DgmciYPbmx7EBkMbPmUnuUX9rSrqgGlZSpW3QbwD8TM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25BE%2597%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%25BF%2583%25E8%2580%2585%25E5%25BE%2597%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E4%25B8%258B%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0ZXdawuzg1PYR2DgmciYPbmx7EBkMbPmUnuUX9rSrqgGlZSpW3QbwD8TM&d=FyOxfEvlGqeE3CGJWKQQl6tywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=dc8dd85b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25BE%2597%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%25BF%2583%25E8%2580%2585%25E5%25BE%2597%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E4%25B8%258B%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0ZXdawuzg1PYR2DgmciYPbmx7EBkMbPmUnuUX9rSrqgGlZSpW3QbwD8TM&h=71afa864\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%BE%97%E6%B0%91%E5%BF%83%E8%80%85%E5%BE%97%E5%A4%A9%E4%B8%8B/?fbclid=IwAR0ZXdawuzg1PYR2DgmciYPbmx7EBkMbPmUnuUX9rSrqgGlZSpW3QbwD8TM</a>"},{"pid":"edcf97b2fcac3cd4af6887c9f2dbd87567c33ebe","tid":2390852,"uid":224510,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T00:21:14.000Z","msg":"話佢哋失民心<br />\n一陣國安法拉佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1853b1cbdcf49f0f5fd980af8dc76bbbb364a71","tid":2390852,"uid":129340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite